{"tid":1399097,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［八五罷工］踏 上 這 無 盡 旅 途！","createTime":"2019-08-03T04:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T06:19:31.000Z","uid":213379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5e8b0e28872916f10f34806c1a79b660af976e8f","tid":1399097,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:52:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全港罷工 七區集會<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n記住爭取到真普選就係贏<br />\n點解? 因為只有真普選 <br />\n幾多訴求都唔係問題</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重申五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1）全面實行雙普選<br />\n2）撤銷所有反送中控罪並承諾永不追究<br />\n3）成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n4）撤銷612暴動定性<br />\n5）撤回逃犯條例</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>攜手開拓一個無盡旅途</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日見到各區既人表現得好勇武<br />\n大家已經有一個反擊既心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nKEEP住呢團火去到八五罷工<br />\n老實講 個日已經預計到<br />\n一定會有衝突發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以你有兩日時間去裝備自己<br />\n口罩眼罩頭盔係基本防具<br />\n其他野餐用品自行準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>裝備須知</strong></span><br />\n最近有個新喪屍GAME IDEA<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1222684\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1222684</a><br />\n<br />\n[推到全人類有豬嘴]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372542\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372542</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>心態決定命運 人數決定一切</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">1） 保持獨立思考能力</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n切勿以訛傳訛<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">成日自我製造白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以一定要fact check</span></span></strong><br />\n如果亂咁share一D未經證實既新聞<br />\n搞到人心惶惶, 嚇自己友做乜撚???<br />\n<br />\n有時候要暫時放棄一D道德觀念<br />\n以無賴手法去對抗呢個無賴政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">今時今日個現況 已經退無可退<br />\n所以我地要贏 就要用盡所有方法去贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">2）「不被捕」係首要</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n下次唔會知被捉走左既義士<br />\n仲會唔會有機會放得返出黎<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">流血受傷已經唔係我地要怕既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地怕既係會失去更多兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以要走一齊走 同埋一定要救人！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n去或留, 所有事, 現場決定<br />\n前線要有哨兵, 長時間留意TG資訊<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">以航拍機/望遠鏡觀察對方人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到速龍準備, 拉住身邊兄弟慢慢後退</span></span></strong><br />\n因為捉到人既主要係速龍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3）克服心中恐懼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n無論你係前線<br />\n見到速龍 暴龍 啟暴龍都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請保持冷靜 唔好淨係諗住走！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">要冷靜地向後面傳達信息</span></span></strong><br />\n試下唔好淨係講「有速龍」<br />\n講下有幾多隻, 佢地係咩狀態<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">要冷靜地向尋找出一個反擊機會</span></span></strong><br />\n以新城市事件為例, <br />\n一個肯打, 十個就會跟住打<br />\n都係個句 人數決定一切<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">4）前線去或留？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n係前線對持到一兩個鐘後,<br />\n對家都應該有所準備<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">要知道我地出黎<br />\n唔係為左守住一個半個街口<br />\n所以薑持到上下就要轉埸</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有一個情況下去落單<br />\n在人數有壓倒勝下<br />\n少鏡頭, 少記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打！但唔好打死D動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">請前線手足熟讀兵法及練習好棍法</span></strong></span><br />\n[置頂]防暴戰術圖文分析，前線入來睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386199\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386199</a><br />\n<br />\n【多圖慎入】【速成】海豹突擊隊短棍訓練<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391145\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391145</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">從來唔只係一個口號 <br />\n而係需要付諸實行<br />\n當公義、法治、價值觀都扭曲晒<br />\n所有原來既自由都失去緊既時候<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">革命 就係我地要做既事！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寧為玉碎 不為瓦全</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為唔知呢場運動會玩到幾耐<br />\n一輸我地就乜都無 所以要令團火燒落去<br />\n燒盡我地所有力氣為止<br />\n請各位留有用之驅 同對家鬥長命<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">就算死 都要死得有價值！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4PACFmxlHm8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4PACFmxlHm8&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsVHO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=82574972\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4PACFmxlHm8</a>"},{"pid":"720cca9cf7e0f8046f995fde4f4e60f690e1564d","tid":1399097,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:53:03.000Z","msg":"同我推上去<br />\n<br />\n「輿論戰」 【都市擂台】對於有市民發起的「不合作運動」，你支持嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/poll/f83b2360-b41c-11e9-8d6b-b77be6568e98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fpoll%2Ff83b2360-b41c-11e9-8d6b-b77be6568e98&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsVHO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=dbed8a84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/poll/f83b2360-b41c-11e9-8d6b-b77be6568e98</a><br />\n<br />\nbetween Chrome 無痕模式 可重複投"},{"pid":"7f9f4c22128b041b8ca8a609c0d1fc608e642cc2","tid":1399097,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:53:34.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n寧為玉碎 不為瓦全"},{"pid":"7f7114e06138459fd1187200921e777c32fdb939","tid":1399097,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n寧為玉碎 不為瓦全"},{"pid":"22c7ff7a03c396d4fcc0c75ae6419cca98cccc7b","tid":1399097,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:53:58.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n寧為玉碎 不為瓦全"},{"pid":"1a36837164449ddb87d4d998ca6ea3d103c6fea8","tid":1399097,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:54:14.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n寧為玉碎 不為瓦全"},{"pid":"527b6616f0dab43861879871506ab10b025c6f11","tid":1399097,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n寧為玉碎 不為瓦全"},{"pid":"c1136405207755ef631f0596a56632c4662c1f14","tid